<i>adverb</i>: 자랑스레 [자랑스레], 떵떵 [떵떵] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>자랑스레 [자랑스레]</dt><br>
<dd>boastfully; proudly</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 드러내어 뽐낼 만한 데가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of showing something to others affectedly.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>떵떵 [떵떵]</dt><br>
<dd>1. with hot air</dd><br>
<dd>함부로 장담하여 말하는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of affirming recklessly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. boastfully; high on the hog</dd><br>
<dd>권세나 재산을 뽐내는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of boasting of one's authority or wealth.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>